          <h3 style="color: #5cb245;">Choose the departure time of your tour</h3><br>
          We advise you to be at least 10 minutes early to prepare your bikes, while you and the guide are getting ready for the tour.<br><br>

          <select name="happy-city-tour-time" id="happ-city-tour-time">
            <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your option...</option>
            <option value="10">10:00</option>
            <option value="11">11:00</option>
            <option value="12">12:00</option>
            <option value="13">13:00</option>
